1
00:00:07,033 --> 00:00:11,233
♪I've braved the storms, walked through the rain♪

2
00:00:11,267 --> 00:00:14,633
♪Seen the highs and lows along the way♪

3
00:00:14,833 --> 00:00:18,033
♪But you stay quiet, never change♪

4
00:00:18,233 --> 00:00:21,633
♪Like a child who dreams beneath the stars♪

5
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:25,033
♪I've read the story in your eyes♪

6
00:00:25,267 --> 00:00:28,533
♪And finally, nothing's left to hide♪

7
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,133
♪You won't give in to a world so cold♪

8
00:00:32,267 --> 00:00:35,733
♪So you wander through it on your own♪

9
00:00:35,867 --> 00:00:39,333
♪Maybe fate has drawn us near♪

10
00:00:39,433 --> 00:00:42,333
♪Just to help you learn to believe♪

11
00:00:42,567 --> 00:00:45,500
♪Everything you've questioned deep inside♪

12
00:00:45,633 --> 00:00:49,733
♪I'll be the proof you need♪

13
00:00:49,867 --> 00:00:51,167
♪I've made my choice♪

14
00:00:51,267 --> 00:00:54,133
♪For you, I'll be brave and break the rules♪

15
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:57,367
♪What's there to fear even if the world is right and I am wrong?♪

16
00:00:58,067 --> 00:01:00,933
♪One day, all of this will turn into memories♪

17
00:01:01,467 --> 00:01:04,367
♪Every storm we faced will turn into our life's scenery♪

18
00:01:05,133 --> 00:01:08,033
♪For you, I'll be brave and break the rules♪

19
00:01:08,333 --> 00:01:11,267
♪What's there to fear even if the world is right and I am wrong?♪

20
00:01:11,967 --> 00:01:14,833
♪Even if, in the end, the whole world turns against me♪

21
00:01:15,333 --> 00:01:18,267
♪I won't regret having loved you♪

22
00:01:18,367 --> 00:01:21,933
♪With all my heart♪

23
00:01:22,167 --> 00:01:25,767
♪I've held you close♪

24
00:01:25,867 --> 00:01:29,467
♪Walked by your side♪

25
00:01:29,633 --> 00:01:33,933
♪And loved the fire that burned inside you♪

26
00:01:33,933 --> 00:01:35,467
[The First Frost]

27
00:01:35,467 --> 00:01:36,967
[Adapted from the novel of the same name by Zhu Yi on www.jjwxc.net]

28
00:01:37,433 --> 00:01:38,700
During the winter holiday

29
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,500
first, stay safe.

30
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:43,133
Also, keep your emotions in check.

31
00:01:43,567 --> 00:01:44,867
Don't just focus on having fun.

32
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:46,867
You're in your first year of high school now.

33
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,600
But before you know it, you'll be in the second year.

34
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,467
What's going to happen next?

35
00:01:50,567 --> 00:01:51,767
Then, the third year will be here.

36
00:01:52,133 --> 00:01:54,267
Are you going to spend three whole years

37
00:01:54,467 --> 00:01:55,933
fighting for the college entrance exam

38
00:01:56,167 --> 00:01:57,500
or just put in the last year's effort?

39
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:58,667
You can calculate it yourself.

40
00:02:03,167 --> 00:02:05,033
The effort you put into your studies

41
00:02:05,033 --> 00:02:06,133
will show

42
00:02:06,133 --> 00:02:07,733
in the results on exam day.

43
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,567
I was pretty impressive when I was your age.

44
00:02:10,567 --> 00:02:12,300
I started putting in the effort back in my first year.

45
00:02:12,633 --> 00:02:13,767
If you listen, it's on you.

46
00:02:13,767 --> 00:02:15,200
If not, it's on me.

47
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:15,800
Class is over!

48
00:02:19,433 --> 00:02:20,367
Why do you

49
00:02:20,933 --> 00:02:21,833
have so few textbooks?

50
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:24,633
I took most of them home

51
00:02:24,633 --> 00:02:25,367
a few days ago.

52
00:02:26,767 --> 00:02:28,000
Even just a few days ago, they were that few.

53
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,400
I started collecting them a few days ago.

54
00:02:30,867 --> 00:02:32,167
I like to study like crazy at home.

55
00:02:33,933 --> 00:02:34,667
You care so much about me?

56
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,767
Sang Yan, let's go play basketball!

57
00:02:40,067 --> 00:02:42,167
Let's crush the guys from No. 2 High School!

58
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:44,800
I'm not going.

59
00:02:45,167 --> 00:02:46,067
I'm heading home

60
00:02:46,367 --> 00:02:47,167
and hitting the books.

61
00:02:52,067 --> 00:02:52,700
Bro

62
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:53,800
did you catch some terminal illness?

63
00:02:54,333 --> 00:02:55,500
Or are you suddenly having a burst of energy

64
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,333
to study?

65
00:02:56,333 --> 00:02:57,067
Whatever happens

66
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,933
I'll give you a big hug.

67
00:03:01,367 --> 00:03:02,233
Are you insane?

68
00:03:02,667 --> 00:03:03,200
Get lost.

69
00:03:04,433 --> 00:03:05,000
Where to?

70
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,733
To the court?

71
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,400
I'm leaving!

72
00:03:06,867 --> 00:03:07,567
Sang Yan!

73
00:03:07,933 --> 00:03:08,833
Sang Yan!

74
00:03:16,667 --> 00:03:22,533
♪Baby, I want to give my all to you♪

75
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:26,567
♪No more tears from now on...♪

76
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:29,833
You're not studying properly anymore

77
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,933
not even playing basketball

78
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:34,433
just learning how to stalk people, huh?

79
00:03:35,267 --> 00:03:36,433
I am...

80
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,767
I am going to take the bus.

81
00:03:38,333 --> 00:03:39,667
I live in the same direction.

82
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:42,767
How come I've never seen you on the bus?

83
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,567
So, you've been

84
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,800
searching for me?

85
00:03:48,067 --> 00:03:50,200
I just mean I don't remember.

86
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,700
Next time, look carefully.

87
00:03:52,933 --> 00:03:54,033
Why should I look carefully?

88
00:03:54,767 --> 00:03:56,367
So you won't miss out

89
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:58,500
the chance to go to school with me.

90
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,833
♪I just want you to know...♪

91
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,600
Where do you live?

92
00:04:03,067 --> 00:04:03,767
What for?

93
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:06,467
Next time when I reach your stop

94
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:07,467
I'll pay more attention.

95
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:15,033
♪To catch you every time you feel vulnerable♪

96
00:04:15,667 --> 00:04:18,767
[Episode 5]
[Get Closer]

97
00:04:19,733 --> 00:04:23,567
♪To protect you♪

98
00:04:24,433 --> 00:04:27,267
♪I love you♪

99
00:04:27,267 --> 00:04:28,167
[3068 days]

100
00:04:41,633 --> 00:04:42,267
Sorry.

101
00:04:42,267 --> 00:04:43,233
I didn't know what you all liked to eat.

102
00:04:43,233 --> 00:04:44,133
So I didn't get anything for you.

103
00:04:44,833 --> 00:04:46,767
I remember you don't like cilantro and garlic.

104
00:04:47,767 --> 00:04:48,333
Thanks.

105
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:54,233
I don't like them either.

106
00:04:55,133 --> 00:04:56,167
Sorry, I forgot.

107
00:04:56,167 --> 00:04:56,933
Let me pick it out for you.

108
00:04:58,033 --> 00:04:58,833
Xiang Lang

109
00:04:59,033 --> 00:05:00,200
you're like you're taking care

110
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,333
of two wives.

111
00:05:03,833 --> 00:05:05,200
Dian, Qiao, and I

112
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,033
have been looking after each other

113
00:05:06,033 --> 00:05:07,167
since kindergarten.

114
00:05:07,167 --> 00:05:08,000
We've been used to it.

115
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,600
I often hear you guys call Wen Yifan "Dian".

116
00:05:11,067 --> 00:05:12,633
Is it her nickname from kindergarten?

117
00:05:13,567 --> 00:05:15,233
Actually, it's a funny story.

118
00:05:15,367 --> 00:05:16,267
Back in kindergarten

119
00:05:16,267 --> 00:05:17,433
she used to write "Yi" in her name as four dots (Dians).

120
00:05:17,433 --> 00:05:18,467
Put them together

121
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,467
and it becomes:

122
00:05:19,467 --> 00:05:21,467
Wen "Dian Dian Dian Dian" Fan.

123
00:05:21,933 --> 00:05:22,500
Wait, no.

124
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,867
It should be called Wen "Dian Dian Dian Dian Dian"

125
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,600
"Fan" also has one dot.

126
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:29,567
Thanks.

127
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:32,900
Done or not?

128
00:05:34,067 --> 00:05:34,600
It's fine.

129
00:05:35,767 --> 00:05:36,333
Look at them.

130
00:05:37,633 --> 00:05:39,000
Look at their family of three.

131
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:41,033
Dian, here.

132
00:05:41,767 --> 00:05:43,333
Now look at us two.

133
00:05:45,167 --> 00:05:45,767
Fine.

134
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,033
Then I'll leave home.

135
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,800
Eat up.

136
00:05:54,933 --> 00:05:56,200
Eating will shut you up.

137
00:05:56,767 --> 00:05:57,767
After eating, we'll go to Overtime.

138
00:05:57,933 --> 00:05:58,900
I reserved a private room for you.

139
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,200
It's a rotating turntable.

140
00:06:23,467 --> 00:06:26,100
[Overtime]

141
00:06:27,133 --> 00:06:27,767
Dian

142
00:06:27,867 --> 00:06:29,867
do you think living with Sang Yan would be miserable?

143
00:06:30,033 --> 00:06:31,067
Why do you ask that?

144
00:06:31,633 --> 00:06:34,167
He didn't even smile while eating just now.

145
00:06:34,167 --> 00:06:36,167
He looked like someone owed him a fortune.

146
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,267
Really?

147
00:06:38,167 --> 00:06:39,333
I feel like

148
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,467
he's pretty proud.

149
00:06:41,667 --> 00:06:43,400
Isn't he always like this?

150
00:06:44,467 --> 00:06:45,233
How about

151
00:06:45,333 --> 00:06:46,633
you live at Xiang Lang's place instead?

152
00:06:48,833 --> 00:06:49,833
What I mean is

153
00:06:49,833 --> 00:06:51,467
you swap places with Xiang Lang.

154
00:06:51,467 --> 00:06:52,833
Let Xiang Lang live with Sang Yan.

155
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,600
I can do that.

156
00:06:57,367 --> 00:06:58,867
Forget it, too much trouble.

157
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,367
They're here.

158
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,000
Let's stop talking about this.

159
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:06,867
Come on, everyone.

160
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,767
Try our new products.

161
00:07:09,333 --> 00:07:10,367
Yu Zhuo, introduce to them.

162
00:07:10,567 --> 00:07:11,633
This cup is for me.

163
00:07:12,033 --> 00:07:13,067
It's called "Allergic to Work."

164
00:07:13,567 --> 00:07:15,400
This cup is called "Paid to Slack off."

165
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:15,900
Thanks.

166
00:07:16,233 --> 00:07:17,000
This cup is called

167
00:07:17,367 --> 00:07:18,667
"Why Overcompetition?"

168
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:20,633
This cup is called

169
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,267
"Reject False Promises."

170
00:07:23,633 --> 00:07:24,433
This cup is called...

171
00:07:24,433 --> 00:07:25,000
Wait a minute.

172
00:07:25,867 --> 00:07:27,567
Who came up with these names?

173
00:07:27,667 --> 00:07:28,867
I did. How's that?

174
00:07:30,067 --> 00:07:30,933
This cup for me is called...

175
00:07:31,067 --> 00:07:32,233
"Better off Skipping the Work."

176
00:07:34,067 --> 00:07:35,633
Let's play Truth or Dare.

177
00:07:35,633 --> 00:07:36,167
What do you think?

178
00:07:36,467 --> 00:07:37,067
Sure.

179
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,167
But do you know how to play?

180
00:07:38,567 --> 00:07:39,633
Who do you think you're looking down on?

181
00:07:39,633 --> 00:07:40,133
Come on.

182
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,567
I don't know how to play.

183
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,267
No worries

184
00:07:42,433 --> 00:07:43,233
We've got your back.

185
00:07:44,267 --> 00:07:45,400
Xiang Lang, you're the guest. You go first.

186
00:07:46,233 --> 00:07:46,800
Here

187
00:07:50,467 --> 00:07:51,033
Five sixs.

188
00:07:51,433 --> 00:07:52,133
Eight sixs.

189
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,133
Ten.

190
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,500
Start.

191
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,433
Start?

192
00:08:05,933 --> 00:08:07,367
This is just the first round

193
00:08:07,367 --> 00:08:08,233
and you're already calling me out?

194
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:11,600
Let's wait and see.

195
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,367
Here

196
00:08:14,433 --> 00:08:15,400
Nine sixs.

197
00:08:15,433 --> 00:08:17,200
Su Haoan, you're off to a bad start.

198
00:08:17,333 --> 00:08:18,333
Truth or Dare?

199
00:08:18,333 --> 00:08:19,567
This is a weird one.

200
00:08:19,567 --> 00:08:20,167
Dare.

201
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,433
Take a look

202
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,667
Choose someone here...

203
00:08:29,133 --> 00:08:29,700
and kiss them.

204
00:08:31,067 --> 00:08:32,367
You're not chickening out

205
00:08:32,567 --> 00:08:33,400
are you?

206
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:34,800
Who said I can't play?

207
00:08:43,767 --> 00:08:44,600
I'll go all in.

208
00:08:45,033 --> 00:08:46,233
Bro

209
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,033
help me out!

210
00:08:47,533 --> 00:08:48,567
Who else would I kiss if not you?

211
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:51,000
You've kissed Duan Jiaxu while playing games in college, haven't you?

212
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,800
Really?

213
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:52,833
You and Duan Jiaxu?

214
00:08:53,067 --> 00:08:54,333
You know him, too?

215
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,667
You forgot I'm also from Nanwu University.

216
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,400
They're in the same department, same class

217
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,467
even the same dorm.

218
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:02,100
They're both Computer Science majors.

219
00:09:08,833 --> 00:09:09,433
Well done!

220
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:10,767
See? I'm brave enough to play.

221
00:09:13,167 --> 00:09:14,200
Let's go. Next round.

222
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,200
Here

223
00:09:20,333 --> 00:09:21,033
Let's go...

224
00:09:21,033 --> 00:09:22,067
Next round.

225
00:09:33,367 --> 00:09:34,033
Six twos.

226
00:09:34,267 --> 00:09:35,033
Six threes.

227
00:09:35,033 --> 00:09:35,800
Seven threes.

228
00:09:35,867 --> 00:09:36,633
Start.

229
00:09:38,567 --> 00:09:39,333
Start?

230
00:09:40,367 --> 00:09:41,400
You're calling it so soon

231
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:41,933
Wen Yifan?

232
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,400
Truth or Dare?

233
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,633
Truth.

234
00:09:48,767 --> 00:09:49,533
Then let me pick for you.

235
00:09:50,933 --> 00:09:53,600
Tell us one good trait

236
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,600
about every man here.

237
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,067
Let's start with Su Haoan.

238
00:10:01,467 --> 00:10:02,267
Rich.

239
00:10:04,167 --> 00:10:04,833
What about Xiang Lang?

240
00:10:07,267 --> 00:10:08,933
Smart, handsome

241
00:10:09,267 --> 00:10:10,200
and considerate.

242
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,167
I thought you were only supposed to say one?

243
00:10:13,567 --> 00:10:14,567
What about Sang Yan?

244
00:10:19,167 --> 00:10:20,000
Calm...

245
00:10:20,567 --> 00:10:21,233
Quiet...

246
00:10:21,633 --> 00:10:22,233
Confident...

247
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:27,833
Just confident.

248
00:10:27,933 --> 00:10:28,567
Too confident.

249
00:10:36,033 --> 00:10:37,067
Twelve sixs.

250
00:10:40,033 --> 00:10:40,567
Dian

251
00:10:41,867 --> 00:10:42,767
don't be too eager...

252
00:10:42,833 --> 00:10:43,667
Fifteen sixs.

253
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:45,100
You really dare to call it?

254
00:10:46,267 --> 00:10:47,867
I dare. Do you dare to open it?

255
00:10:48,033 --> 00:10:48,933
What's there to be afraid of?

256
00:10:49,033 --> 00:10:49,700
Open it.

257
00:10:58,367 --> 00:10:59,167
Five sixs.

258
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:00,833
You won!

259
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,933
Xiang Lang, I told you!

260
00:11:04,267 --> 00:11:05,167
You fell for his trick.

261
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,867
Truth or Dare?

262
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,767
Truth.

263
00:11:09,833 --> 00:11:12,600
Tell us one thing you regret the most.

264
00:11:13,767 --> 00:11:14,933
The biggest regret?

265
00:11:15,867 --> 00:11:17,567
It's probably studying abroad.

266
00:11:17,867 --> 00:11:19,367
I was supposed to go to Yihe University

267
00:11:19,567 --> 00:11:20,533
with Dian.

268
00:11:24,933 --> 00:11:25,633
Why did you choose Yihe University?

269
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,533
I had already made plans with someone else.

270
00:11:29,933 --> 00:11:32,267
Dian was supposed to go to Nanwu University with me.

271
00:11:32,267 --> 00:11:34,033
Who knew she suddenly went to Yihe University.

272
00:11:34,867 --> 00:11:35,933
I had already applied

273
00:11:35,933 --> 00:11:38,267
for the best program at Yihe, Clinical Medicine

274
00:11:38,833 --> 00:11:40,667
but my parents insisted I go abroad.

275
00:11:41,233 --> 00:11:43,233
Otherwise, from kindergarten to university

276
00:11:43,767 --> 00:11:44,767
we would have been classmates the whole time.

277
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,400
Real childhood sweethearts.

278
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,200
Let's continue.

279
00:11:57,467 --> 00:11:58,400
Yes, let's continue.

280
00:11:58,933 --> 00:12:00,067
Let's make this round more exciting.

281
00:12:00,367 --> 00:12:01,333
We'll double the penalty for the loser

282
00:12:01,567 --> 00:12:02,767
both Truth and Dare.

283
00:12:02,767 --> 00:12:03,267
What do you think?

284
00:12:06,267 --> 00:12:06,833
Six threes.

285
00:12:07,433 --> 00:12:08,200
Ten fours.

286
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:09,933
Ten fives!

287
00:12:15,467 --> 00:12:18,933
Fifteen...

288
00:12:18,933 --> 00:12:19,767
Twenty sixs.

289
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,700
Start.

290
00:12:34,433 --> 00:12:34,933
I lost.

291
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:36,400
Yeah, you finally lost.

292
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,267
No regrets in my life.

293
00:12:37,267 --> 00:12:39,400
Come on, Truth and Dare.

294
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,600
Let's do truth first.

295
00:12:43,933 --> 00:12:44,933
The last city

296
00:12:45,167 --> 00:12:46,700
you flew to?

297
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:47,600
What a boring question.

298
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,267
Who cares?

299
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:50,400
Yihe.

300
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,067
You paid for the bill, right?

301
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,200
Let's split it three ways.

302
00:13:26,667 --> 00:13:27,633
The front desk said

303
00:13:27,633 --> 00:13:28,367
Sang Yan already paid.

304
00:13:29,567 --> 00:13:30,467
He did?

305
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:33,167
I thought Sang Yan only gave a 90% discount

306
00:13:33,167 --> 00:13:34,067
and he was so stingy.

307
00:13:34,067 --> 00:13:35,333
Looks like I wrongly accused him.

308
00:13:36,033 --> 00:13:36,700
How about

309
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,100
we leave a five-star review for him?

310
00:13:38,333 --> 00:13:40,033
We can't take advantage of him for free.

311
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,467
I'll take a call.

312
00:13:42,433 --> 00:13:43,400
Hello, Ms. Qian?

313
00:13:44,833 --> 00:13:45,833
Okay, I got it.

314
00:13:46,167 --> 00:13:47,333
I'll take care of it right away.

315
00:13:49,833 --> 00:13:51,467
I got an urgent task.

316
00:13:51,467 --> 00:13:52,600
I need to go home and finish an article.

317
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,000
Let me give you a ride.

318
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:54,600
You'll get home faster.

319
00:13:54,767 --> 00:13:55,267
Sure.

320
00:13:55,767 --> 00:13:57,467
Take care.

321
00:13:57,467 --> 00:13:58,700
I'll take a few pictures for him.

322
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:00,000
Okay. Bye.

323
00:14:00,700 --> 00:14:01,233
Bye.

324
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:04,000
Be careful on your way.

325
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:05,467
Okay. You take care, too.

326
00:14:08,267 --> 00:14:09,033
Let's go.

327
00:14:26,467 --> 00:14:27,000
Zhong Siqiao!

328
00:14:28,067 --> 00:14:28,833
Why are you still here?

329
00:14:30,467 --> 00:14:31,833
You already treated us.

330
00:14:31,833 --> 00:14:33,367
Shouldn't I take some photos for you

331
00:14:33,367 --> 00:14:34,167
and recommend it?

332
00:14:34,533 --> 00:14:35,200
It's great.

333
00:14:36,233 --> 00:14:37,233
Let me buy you another drink.

334
00:14:39,067 --> 00:14:39,800
Wait a minute.

335
00:14:40,333 --> 00:14:40,933
What's up?

336
00:14:41,933 --> 00:14:43,067
Didn't we agree

337
00:14:43,067 --> 00:14:44,867
we wouldn't drink together again?

338
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:48,267
Right.

339
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:51,833
You drink then.

340
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:52,933
You're the guest.

341
00:14:54,467 --> 00:14:55,367
Or you drink.

342
00:14:55,367 --> 00:14:56,333
You just had a breakup.

343
00:14:56,333 --> 00:14:57,433
Let the alcohol cure your sorrow.

344
00:14:58,467 --> 00:14:59,767
One drink's enough.

345
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:01,700
I can't keep using alcohol to drown my sorrows.

346
00:15:06,567 --> 00:15:07,167
Let me ask you

347
00:15:08,167 --> 00:15:09,833
don't you feel like everyone's acting a little strange today?

348
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,033
Yeah, a little.

349
00:15:16,933 --> 00:15:17,800
Let me ask you again

350
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:20,000
why didn't Wen Yifan go to Nanwu University?

351
00:15:20,767 --> 00:15:22,233
Her grades are so much higher.

352
00:15:23,933 --> 00:15:25,567
I'm her good friend

353
00:15:25,933 --> 00:15:27,367
but I don't get it either.

354
00:15:27,767 --> 00:15:29,067
I feel like she just wants

355
00:15:29,067 --> 00:15:30,633
to keep her distance from everyone.

356
00:15:30,633 --> 00:15:31,933
Even I haven't heard from her much.

357
00:15:33,367 --> 00:15:34,233
I thought

358
00:15:34,467 --> 00:15:35,333
when people grow up

359
00:15:35,333 --> 00:15:36,600
their feelings change.

360
00:15:37,233 --> 00:15:38,933
I really hate this change.

361
00:15:41,467 --> 00:15:42,267
Do you believe me?

362
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:44,500
Every time I date

363
00:15:44,567 --> 00:15:46,600
I hope the current one is the last.

364
00:15:47,433 --> 00:15:48,533
But nowadays

365
00:15:48,667 --> 00:15:49,800
no one believes

366
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,933
that love should be timeless.

367
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,400
If you keep acting like this

368
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:54,033
It'll put a lot of pressure on your partner.

369
00:15:55,033 --> 00:15:56,533
What's wrong with wanting to spend a lifetime together?

370
00:16:00,667 --> 00:16:02,567
Maybe you just haven't met the right person yet.

371
00:16:02,567 --> 00:16:03,867
It's you who hasn't met the right person.

372
00:16:04,433 --> 00:16:05,533
Why are you pulling me into this?

373
00:16:05,833 --> 00:16:06,967
I'd rather not date

374
00:16:06,967 --> 00:16:07,833
than settle for the wrong person.

375
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,667
You're still not going home?

376
00:16:26,267 --> 00:16:26,867
What about them?

377
00:16:27,933 --> 00:16:28,667
They've gone back.

378
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,367
I want to ask you something.

379
00:16:32,633 --> 00:16:33,633
You still like Wen Yifan, right?

380
00:16:37,767 --> 00:16:39,467
I just feel like you still have feelings for her.

381
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,600
That's why I tried to set you up to be roommates.

382
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,833
I've said this so many times.

383
00:16:47,233 --> 00:16:47,867
We're roommates

384
00:16:48,533 --> 00:16:49,267
just roommates.

385
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,433
Enough.

386
00:16:53,067 --> 00:16:54,067
I can tell

387
00:16:54,067 --> 00:16:55,267
you're not okay.

388
00:16:58,633 --> 00:16:59,467
For example?

389
00:17:00,033 --> 00:17:00,833
What's not okay?

390
00:17:02,467 --> 00:17:03,467
The way you looked at Xiang Lang.

391
00:17:03,467 --> 00:17:04,433
You didn't like

392
00:17:04,433 --> 00:17:05,533
anything about him.

393
00:17:05,533 --> 00:17:06,900
Weren't you jealous of him?

394
00:17:11,567 --> 00:17:12,567
Are you insane?

395
00:17:15,033 --> 00:17:16,067
Keep being stubborn.

396
00:17:17,067 --> 00:17:19,033
I've seen you in this awful state before, after all.

397
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:20,867
The last time

398
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:22,833
was the day the college entrance results came out.

399
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,633
Do you still remember?

400
00:17:31,133 --> 00:17:38,733
[Beiyu]

401
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:45,367
You've been quite busy lately, haven't you?

402
00:17:45,667 --> 00:17:47,100
I've been unable to reach you.

403
00:17:48,167 --> 00:17:49,200
What happened to you?

404
00:17:51,033 --> 00:17:51,633
Nothing.

405
00:17:52,967 --> 00:17:53,900
My phone broke.

406
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,200
Why are you here?

407
00:18:14,367 --> 00:18:15,167
Earlier

408
00:18:15,533 --> 00:18:16,400
didn't we agree on this?

409
00:18:17,267 --> 00:18:18,767
After the admission results come out

410
00:18:18,767 --> 00:18:19,600
I'd come to visit.

411
00:18:20,833 --> 00:18:21,633
My results are in.

412
00:18:22,667 --> 00:18:23,333
I got into Nanwu University

413
00:18:23,533 --> 00:18:24,433
Computer Science department.

414
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,333
Your grades are better than mine.

415
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:28,000
You'll easily get into the program you want...

416
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:28,633
Sang Yan

417
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,167
I didn't apply to Nanwu University.

418
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,800
You're kidding, right?

419
00:18:37,867 --> 00:18:38,433
No.

420
00:18:41,567 --> 00:18:42,533
Then where did you apply?

421
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:45,800
Yihe University.

422
00:18:48,867 --> 00:18:49,467
Why?

423
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,567
Why Yihe University?

424
00:18:57,600 --> 00:18:58,967
I had already made plans with someone else.

425
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,267
You came back so late. Our parents will be concerned.

426
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,633
Do you want some jelly?

427
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,433
Haoan is already waiting for you.

428
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:10,467
Does Haoan want some jelly, too?

429
00:19:26,767 --> 00:19:27,567
What about me?

430
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:30,433
Don't you want to say anything to me?

431
00:19:32,167 --> 00:19:33,367
Well, I'll say it straight.

432
00:19:34,867 --> 00:19:35,600
Sang Yan

433
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,467
I really hate it

434
00:19:39,867 --> 00:19:41,267
and I really dislike it

435
00:19:42,033 --> 00:19:43,567
that you always come looking for me in Beiyu.

436
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,400
It's annoying

437
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,867
to come out to meet you every time.

438
00:19:53,867 --> 00:19:54,633
Wen Yifan

439
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:00,400
am I just your backup option?

440
00:20:03,667 --> 00:20:04,900
Nanwu is closer to Beiyu.

441
00:20:05,267 --> 00:20:06,867
So, I'll go somewhere farther away.

442
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,200
When I get to Yihe

443
00:20:10,067 --> 00:20:11,467
I hope you won't come looking for me

444
00:20:11,467 --> 00:20:12,400
like this anymore.

445
00:20:16,733 --> 00:20:17,567
You're back.

446
00:20:19,867 --> 00:20:21,200
You didn't reply on WeChat

447
00:20:21,367 --> 00:20:22,600
and didn't answer my calls.

448
00:20:23,667 --> 00:20:25,000
Where have you been?

449
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:26,567
What are you doing here?

450
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:36,233
I got into Nanwu University.

451
00:20:37,567 --> 00:20:39,400
Nanwu University!

452
00:20:45,267 --> 00:20:46,200
What's your attitude about this?

453
00:20:52,367 --> 00:20:53,367
Bro, think about it.

454
00:20:53,467 --> 00:20:54,967
We can still be classmates!

455
00:20:54,967 --> 00:20:56,400
You know how bad my grades were.

456
00:20:56,633 --> 00:20:57,967
Getting into Nanwu University

457
00:20:57,967 --> 00:20:59,567
will make my grandparents so happy!

458
00:21:00,267 --> 00:21:00,867
You know what?

459
00:21:00,867 --> 00:21:02,767
When you said you were going to Nanwu University

460
00:21:02,767 --> 00:21:03,400
I thought

461
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,167
how good is Nanwu University?

462
00:21:04,167 --> 00:21:04,800
Still playing games?

463
00:21:37,033 --> 00:21:37,667
Dian.

464
00:21:42,167 --> 00:21:42,767
Nothing.

465
00:21:52,033 --> 00:21:53,333
You're still the same as before.

466
00:21:55,533 --> 00:21:56,600
It seems nothing matters

467
00:21:56,967 --> 00:21:57,833
to you

468
00:21:59,567 --> 00:22:00,567
and you're not interested

469
00:22:01,067 --> 00:22:02,033
in anything.

470
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,033
I'm actually quite curious.

471
00:22:04,967 --> 00:22:06,033
What exactly would it take

472
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,567
to get your attention?

473
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,533
It's not as exaggerated as you say.

474
00:22:12,833 --> 00:22:13,867
Then tell me

475
00:22:15,133 --> 00:22:16,267
how's it been

476
00:22:17,333 --> 00:22:18,067
since you returned to Nanwu?

477
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:19,100
Pretty good.

478
00:22:22,033 --> 00:22:23,167
Always "pretty good."

479
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,333
Every time I ask, it's always "pretty good".

480
00:22:26,067 --> 00:22:27,533
When I was abroad, you were just as half-hearted.

481
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,433
In our group of three

482
00:22:29,633 --> 00:22:30,900
only Qiao and I were talking.

483
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,400
You always just replied something

484
00:22:33,633 --> 00:22:35,667
like "Okay

485
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,633
You never talk about your own stuff.

486
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,867
My life is pretty boring.

487
00:22:41,967 --> 00:22:43,000
Even boring things can be talked about.

488
00:22:46,767 --> 00:22:48,000
Our world is like this

489
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:49,367
if we're happy, we laugh;

490
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:50,600
if we're sad, we cry.

491
00:22:53,267 --> 00:22:55,200
You seem like someone from a completely different world.

492
00:23:04,767 --> 00:23:05,433
Dian

493
00:23:07,067 --> 00:23:08,200
can you promise me one thing?

494
00:23:10,667 --> 00:23:11,433
What is it?

495
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,233
In the future

496
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:15,900
if you encounter

497
00:23:16,167 --> 00:23:17,233
any difficulties

498
00:23:18,067 --> 00:23:19,167
tell me right away.

499
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,533
I don't want you

500
00:23:22,533 --> 00:23:24,433
to always shut me out.

501
00:23:27,267 --> 00:23:27,867
Okay.

502
00:23:29,733 --> 00:23:30,900
Can you explain one thing?

503
00:23:31,233 --> 00:23:33,333
You always wanted to go

504
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:34,833
to Nanwu University.

505
00:23:35,267 --> 00:23:36,267
Why did you end up

506
00:23:36,533 --> 00:23:38,867
quietly switching to Yihe University?

507
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:41,833
Don't you feel regretful?

508
00:23:46,767 --> 00:23:48,167
You know it's a regret

509
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,467
then why bring it up again?

510
00:23:55,533 --> 00:23:56,100
Hey

511
00:23:56,333 --> 00:23:57,800
when are you two going to Nanwu University?

512
00:23:58,067 --> 00:23:58,867
Didn't I tell you?

513
00:23:58,867 --> 00:23:59,800
We're leaving tomorrow.

514
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:02,633
We did it!

515
00:24:02,633 --> 00:24:04,400
- Shout it louder! - We did it!

516
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,667
We did it!

517
00:24:12,833 --> 00:24:14,400
One, two, three!

518
00:24:17,467 --> 00:24:19,233
I will definitely get into Nanwu University.

519
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:21,533
And I believe you will, too.

520
00:24:24,033 --> 00:24:25,333
So let's make a promise

521
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:26,767
to work hard together

522
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,533
and get into Nanwu University.

523
00:24:31,667 --> 00:24:33,267
I will definitely get into Nanwu University.

524
00:24:35,667 --> 00:24:36,533
I'll take your basketball.

525
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:37,600
Why?

526
00:24:38,333 --> 00:24:39,800
Why? Focus on studying!

527
00:24:40,167 --> 00:24:41,333
Don't you want to get into Nanwu University?

528
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,467
Didn't we agree to report?

529
00:25:32,767 --> 00:25:35,067
[I won't come back tonight. Just lock the door.]

530
00:25:38,933 --> 00:25:46,067
[You really keep your promises.]

531
00:25:47,367 --> 00:25:50,900
♪Another drink as night falls♪

532
00:25:52,933 --> 00:25:57,533
♪Let the weariness spread comfortably♪

533
00:25:57,533 --> 00:26:00,267
[Okay.]

534
00:26:00,833 --> 00:26:04,533
♪From my heart to my whole being♪

535
00:26:04,533 --> 00:26:06,300
[I won't come back tonight. Just lock the door. Okay.]

536
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:11,367
♪From the sights before me to the vast world♪

537
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:19,133
♪Like every yesterday♪

538
00:26:20,133 --> 00:26:25,667
♪Fighting off the long night with a celebration♪

539
00:26:28,333 --> 00:26:33,367
♪Others don't need to understand♪

540
00:26:33,467 --> 00:26:38,333
♪The huge difference in my eyes♪

541
00:26:38,533 --> 00:26:40,500
[I won't come back tonight. Just lock the door. Okay.]

542
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:50,067
♪For a fleeting moment, I fall in love with this world...♪

543
00:26:50,433 --> 00:26:51,100
Zhang

544
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:53,233
we have eight topics to choose from this time.

545
00:26:53,233 --> 00:26:55,000
I'll do the first four with Yifan.

546
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,600
You two can do the rest.

547
00:26:58,767 --> 00:27:03,633
♪For a fleeting moment, I make peace with myself♪

548
00:27:04,433 --> 00:27:09,233
♪But this version of me exists only tonight♪

549
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:23,333
♪Only tonight♪

550
00:27:26,967 --> 00:27:32,300
♪Until I find the courage to be kind to myself♪

551
00:27:34,033 --> 00:27:38,033
♪Only tonight♪

552
00:27:38,033 --> 00:27:41,100
[Sang Yan: Not coming back tonight. Lock the door. Wen Yifan: Okay.]

553
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:46,133
[To the battlefield]

554
00:27:53,433 --> 00:27:55,000
The potatoes here are really delicious.

555
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:56,033
Want to try a piece?

556
00:27:59,967 --> 00:28:01,433
Your roommate finally replied to your WeChat?

557
00:28:05,700 --> 00:28:08,367
[Not coming back tonight. Lock the door. Okay.]

558
00:28:21,833 --> 00:28:22,533
Yan

559
00:28:23,167 --> 00:28:24,067
you're so early today.

560
00:28:24,067 --> 00:28:25,467
Isn't school just starting?

561
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:27,967
It's the second year of high school.

562
00:28:27,967 --> 00:28:29,400
If I go early, I can learn a bit more.

563
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,833
But I haven't even made breakfast yet.

564
00:28:30,967 --> 00:28:32,367
I'll buy something on the way.

565
00:28:32,567 --> 00:28:33,067
I'm off.

566
00:28:33,100 --> 00:28:33,867
Take it easy.

567
00:28:47,633 --> 00:28:49,967
♪Caught off guard♪

568
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:53,500
♪Meeting you made me start acting foolish♪

569
00:28:54,067 --> 00:28:57,533
♪My heart races, and even my breath pauses♪

570
