590
00:30:15,267 --> 00:30:16,200
If I sit for too long

591
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:16,767
My legs will fall asleep.

592
00:30:18,333 --> 00:30:21,433
♪Our relationship is spiraling out of control...♪

593
00:30:22,033 --> 00:30:25,433
