someone's looking for you.

611
00:31:36,267 --> 00:31:37,033
She's waiting over there.

612
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:39,567
Jiang

613
00:31:40,533 --> 00:31:42,333
I thought you were still at Yihe.

614
00:31:42,833 --> 00:31:43,800
How long have you been here?

615
00:31:44,533 --> 00:31:46,267
Return the equipment first.

616
00:31:46,267 --> 00:31:46,767
Okay.

617
00:31:46,767 --> 00:31:47,467
Thank you.

618
00:31:55,233 --> 00:31:57,233
I heard from Jia

619
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,267
that she saw you at the city hospital.

620
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,333
I saw your equipment bag

621
00:32:01,333 --> 00:32:02,267
with the TV station logo on it.

622
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:05,200
So I came over to try my luck.

623
00:32:06,667 --> 00:32:07,767
What do you need me for?

624
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,367
It's Little New Year today, right?

625
00:32:11,733 --> 00:32:13,200
And Spring Festival is almost here.

626
00:32:15,033 --> 00:32:16,900
How about spending New Year's Eve at my place?

627
00:32:17,667 --> 00:32:19,167
Also, I want to introduce

628
00:32:19,167 --> 00:32:20,233
someone to you.

629
00:32:20,333 --> 00:32:21,533
I'm fine on my own.

630
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,367
You don't need to worry about me.

631
00:32:22,367 --> 00:32:23,967
That's not what I meant.

632
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,400
You'll understand when you get here.

633
00:32:26,433 --> 00:32:28,833
Jia also asked me to invite you.

634
00:32:34,167 --> 00:32:36,267
Looks like you got approval from Zheng Kejia.

635
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:40,900
Um...

636
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:42,433
I was worried about

637
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:43,767
