638
00:32:43,767 --> 00:32:45,200
I didn't want it to affect your emotions.

639
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:45,800
That's why

640
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,233
I first asked Jia.

641
00:32:49,733 --> 00:32:50,567
I'll go to work now.

642
00:32:50,867 --> 00:32:51,533
Jiang!

643
00:32:53,067 --> 00:32:53,600
Are you...

644
00:32:54,467 --> 00:32:56,433
are you still mad at me?

645
00:32:57,633 --> 00:32:59,233
I know that all these years

646
00:32:59,233 --> 00:33:00,833
I've owed you too much.

647
00:33:03,733 --> 00:33:04,267
How...

648
00:33:04,467 --> 00:33:06,633
